ng and recruiting prospective graduate students. The Upgrid service is designed to help you maximize the potential returns of an informative and easy-to-navigate website. We will review your program website, as well as the websites of your competitors, and collate our findings into two types of easily digestible consulting reports in the client\'s’ web portal created by GET.\r\n\r\n[ms_divider style=\"dashed\" align=\"center\" width=\"100%\" margin_top=\"30px\" margin_bottom=\"30px\" border_size=\"\" border_color=\"\" icon=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]\r\n<h3 class=\"page-title-h3\">The “whoops” report</h3>\r\n\r\nThe first type of report is focused on resolving technical and informational issues that prevent prospective students from obtaining the information they are looking for. By conducting detailed reviews of thousands of graduate program websites, we are experts in the industry standards, and can help you avoid common problems such as typo, dead links, infinite loops, outdated information, inconsistencies, floating pages, dysfunctional menu or sidebars and confusing information.\r\n[ms_divider style=\"dashed\" align=\"center\" width=\"100%\" margin_top=\"30px\" margin_bottom=\"30px\" border_size=\"\" border_color=\"\" icon=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]\r\n<h3 class=\"page-title-h3\">The enhancement report</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\nThe second type of report compares our client’s program website with that of its direct competitors to provide recommendations for improvement so that clients stay abreast of how competing programs market themselves. The enhancement report is grouped around 6 key areas that we have identified as game changers for successful recruitment. These range from general stylistic issues commonly found in the program introduction to more granular, detailed information such as scholarship information, credit transfer policies and so forth.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nOur Upgrid service is <i>not</i> just a one time service, but a SaaS (Software as a Service). Once we have provided the “whoops” and enhancement reports, we will continue to update the information daily until the contract expiration date (typically the end of the academic year). Our account managers are also available on demand to answer client questions and address any concerns that arise during the service delivery process.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.gridet.com/contact\" style=\"font-weight:500;\"><i class=\"fa fa-lightbulb-o \" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>&nbsp;Request a demo</a>','Upgrid Service','','publish','closed','closed','','upgrid-service','','','2016-07-01 11:21:19','2016-07-01 15:21:19','',57,'http://www.gridet.com/?page_id=69',0,'page','',0),(70,1,'2016-06-15 15:40:32','2016-06-15 19:40:32','Hi, this is the upgrid.','Upgrid Service','','inherit','closed','closed','','69-revision-v1','','','2016-06-15 15:40:32','2016-06-15 19:40:32','',69,'http://www.gridet.com/69-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(71,1,'2016-06-15 15:41:02','2016-06-15 19:41:02','<h2 class=\"page-title-h2\">Gradgrid Graduate Programs Database</h2>\r\n<hr />\r\n&nbsp;\r\nIf you went to college in the United States, you are probably familiar with college guidebooks, campus tours, and college guidance counselors. Unfortunately for graduate school applicants, such resources are only part of the norm. Compared with the accessible and streamlined resources available to prospective undergraduates, efficient and digestible information about graduate schools can be surprisingly difficult to locate or organize. The reasons are many. For example, the graduate programs that you might be interested in, or match your backgrounds could be many, even in different academic fields. To make the best decision, most of the serious degree seekers would dig into the nitty-gritty information and piece the puzzles together.\r\n&nbsp;\r\nOur Gradgrid Database is a free and convenient cloud based solution to the problem of deciding which graduate schools are right for you. Prospective graduate students routinely spend weeks or even months searching the internet for information that will help them sift through the thousands of programs offered by U.S. graduate schools. The Gradgrid database is an advanced, centralized search engine, exclusively devoted to helping applicants find and research programs that interest them.  Both search functions and results are easily customizable. Search results are organized in the ‘grid’ view for easy access and comparison. Your ‘grid’ also allows to customize the information by adding notes and comments of your own.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 500; \">Launching schedule: Fall 2016 </span>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 500;\">Welcome to <a id=\"bookmark-this\"><i class=\"fa fa-bookmark lg\"></i>&nbsp;bookmark</a> and visit us back!</span>','Gradgrid service','','publish','closed','closed','','gradgrid-service','','','2016-07-01 11:09:40','2016-07-01 15:09:40','',57,'http://www.gridet.com/?page_id=71',0,'page','',0),(72,1,'2016-06-15 15:41:02','2016-06-15 19:41:02','Hi, this is the gradgrid service.','Gradgrid services','','inherit','closed','closed','','71-revision-v1','','','2016-06-15 15:41:02','2016-06-15 19:41:02','',71,'http://www.gridet.com/71-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(73,1,'2016-06-15 15:41:42','2016-06-15 19:41:42',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','73','','','2016-07-01 15:00:21','2016-07-01 19:00:21','',57,'http://www.gridet.com/?p=73',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(74,1,'2016-06-15 15:41:42','2016-06-15 19:41:42',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','74','','','2016-07-01 15:00:21','2016-07-01 19:00:21','',57,'http://www.gridet.com/?p=74',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(78,1,'2016-06-15 17:02:55','2016-06-15 21:02:55','Hi, this is the upgrid.\r\n\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed ut dolor vel tellus maximus dapibus. Proin vel nulla vitae nisi tempus fermentum nec at quam. Cras ac odio sagittis, interdum nulla ornare, ornare elit.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->Duis at neque id vel