. in Education Technology and Media from Columbia University in 2012.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"zp\">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n[ms_divider style=\"dashed\" align=\"center\" width=\"100%\" margin_top=\"30px\" margin_bottom=\"30px\" border_size=\"\" border_color=\"\" icon=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]\r\n<h3 class=\"page-title-h3\">Ping Zhang, Ph.D.,</h3>\r\n<h3 class=\"page-title-h3\" style=\"font-size: 1.1rem;color: #888888;font-weight:300;\">Director of Development</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<div><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-527 teampic\" src=\"http://www.gridet.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/zhangping500-300x300.png\" alt=\"zhangping500\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" /></div>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:Garamond, serif; font-size:2rem; color:#333; font-weight\"500;\">P</span>ing Zhang manages the development and maintenance of all products and services. His expertise are in web product development and front and back design. Ping Zhang previously worked at the Cloud Based Computing Center at Amazon from 2011 to 2016. He received his B.E. from Beijing institute of Technology in 2003 and his PhD in Computer Science from Purdue University in 2011.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"wy\">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n[ms_divider style=\"dashed\" align=\"center\" width=\"100%\" margin_top=\"30px\" margin_bottom=\"30px\" border_size=\"\" border_color=\"\" icon=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]\r\n<h3 class=\"page-title-h3\">Vivian Wang, M.A.,</h3>\r\n<h3 class=\"page-title-h3\" style=\"font-size: 1.1rem;color: #888888;font-weight:300;\">Knowledge Director</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-526 teampic\" src=\"http://www.gridet.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/wangyu500-300x300.png\" alt=\"wangyu500\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" /><span style=\"font-family:Garamond, serif; font-size:2rem; color:#333; font-weight\"500;\">V</span>ivian Wang manages the Gradgrid database and oversees a team of knowledge experts. She has extensive professional experience in graduate recruitment, program management, teaching, and advising at universities throughout the world. Vivian Wang previously served as the international program officer first at Xiamen University from 2013 to 2014 and then at Columbia University in 2015. She received a B.A. in Administrative Management from Beijing Electronic Science University in 2009 and an M.A. in Simultaneous Interpreting from Newcastle University in 2010.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"vb\">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n[ms_divider style=\"dashed\" align=\"center\" width=\"100%\" margin_top=\"30px\" margin_bottom=\"30px\" border_size=\"\" border_color=\"\" icon=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]\r\n<h3 class=\"page-title-h3\">Virgilio Bisio, M.A.,</h3>\r\n<h3 class=\"page-title-h3\" style=\"font-size: 1.1rem;color: #888888;font-weight:300;\">Director of Marketing</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-525 teampic\" src=\"http://www.gridet.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/virgil500-300x300.png\" alt=\"virgil500\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" /><span style=\"font-family:Garamond, serif; font-size:2rem; color:#333; font-weight\"500;\">V</span>irgilio Bisio supervises sales, marketing, and client services. From 2012 to 2014 Virgilio worked in operations management for Payton Technology. He received an B.A. in History from Trinity College in 2012 and an M.A. in East Asian Languages and Cultures from Columbia University in 2016.\r\n<div id=\"mn\">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n[ms_divider style=\"dashed\" align=\"center\" width=\"100%\" margin_top=\"30px\" margin_bottom=\"30px\" border_size=\"\" border_color=\"\" icon=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]\r\n<h3 class=\"page-title-h3\">Michael Nusbaum, M.A.,</h3>\r\n<h3 class=\"page-title-h3\" style=\"font-size: 1.1rem;color: #888888;font-weight:300;\">Product Manager</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-524 teampic\" src=\"http://www.gridet.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/michael-500-300x300.png\" alt=\"michael-500\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" /><span style=\