tomizable. Search results are organized in the ‘grid’ view for easy access and comparison. Your ‘grid’ also allows to customize the information by adding notes and comments of your own.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 500; \">Launching schedule: Fall 2016 </span>\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 500;\">Welcome to <a id=\"bookmark-this\"><i class=\"fa fa-bookmark lg\"></i>&nbsp;bookmark</a> and visit us back!</span>','Gradgrid service','','inherit','closed','closed','','71-revision-v1','','','2016-06-30 01:38:53','2016-06-30 05:38:53','',71,'http://www.gridet.com/71-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(514,1,'2016-06-30 10:34:28','2016-06-30 14:34:28','<h2 class=\"page-title-h2\">Upgrid Consulting - Software as a Service</h2>\r\n<hr />\r\n&nbsp;\r\nUpgrid is a website content review, research and consulting service offered by GET to graduate institutions throughout the United States. Graduate program websites are one of the most important tools for attracting and recruiting prospective graduate students. The Upgrid service is designed to help you maximize the potential returns of an informative and easy-to-navigate website. We will review your program website, as well as the websites of your competitors, and collate our findings into two types of easily digestible consulting reports in the client\'s’ web portal created by GET.\r\n\r\n[ms_divider style=\"dashed\" align=\"center\" width=\"100%\" margin_top=\"30px\" margin_bottom=\"30px\" border_size=\"\" border_color=\"\" icon=\"\" class=\"\" id=\"\"]\r\n<h3 class=\"page-title-h3\">The “whoops” report</h3>\r\n\r\nThe first type of report is focused on resolving technical and informational issues that prevent prospective students from obtaining the information they are looking for. By conducting detailed reviews of thousands of graduate program websites, we are experts in the industry standards, and can help you avoid common problems such as typo, dead links, infinite loops, outdated information, inconsistencie